	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Many European-developed games (like those by Eurocom) have all emphasis bits set, making the graphics disappear on RGB PPUs too.  The list includes games like Felix the cat, James Bond Jr, Dropzone, Noah's Ark, etc...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


